GIVEAWAY ! Iceland Review.
We are happy to announce that we are giving away FOUR 1-year subscriptions to our Instagram friends. 
Iceland Review is the longest running magazine presenting Iceland, in continuous print since 1963. Check out our website for more information.
We ship WORLDWIDE so this giveaway is open to everyone! 
_______
HOW TO ENTER:
1. Follow our Instagram page.
2. Like this post.
3. Tag a Iceland-loving friend in a comment. (You and your friend could each win a subscription). _______
This giveaway is in no way endorsed or sponsored by Instagram.
Contest closes at 13:00 (1pm)(GMT) on the 16th of December and winners will be announced on the same day. 
_______
Winners will be contacted for further information regarding delivery (no shipping cost).

On Friday, everything changed for Grindav√≠k. After a surge of earthquakes during the day, the town had to be evacuated later that night, as it became clear that the magma dike had extended below the community. The evacuation was historic - the largest of its kind since the 1973 eruption on Heimaey. Now, the whole of Iceland, and most importantly, the citizens of Grindav√≠k, are awaiting nature‚Äôs next move.
